data.description: ROCKING RANCH! Discover the epitome of comfortable living in the serene and picturesque community of Woodlege Village. This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch home is nestled on a sprawling 1+ acre wooded property, offering tranquility and ample space for both family and friends.The kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite counters, is a culinary haven, providing everything you need for delightful meals. The residence, deceptively large, boasts multiple gathering spaces, ensuring there's room for everyone to come together.Step into a warm and strikingly decorated interior that exudes a welcoming atmosphere. This spacious home features an epic home office, a massive lower level, a convenient 2-car garage, and a main-floor laundry room, catering to all your practical needs.Outdoor living takes center stage with a generous garage rooftop patio, complete with a masonry fireplace, just steps away from a backyard pool--an ideal setting for relaxation and entertaining. All of this is discreetly tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac, offering a peaceful retreat just minutes from the shores of Lake Wallenpaupack.Don't miss the chance to make this your home--schedule a viewing and stop searching, as this property embodies the perfect blend of comfort and lifestyle.
